    "Consequently, a more challenging and reliably assessed SVAMP dataset is introduced.",
    "This dataset adapts examples from pre-existing datasets to evaluate the models' sensitivity to problem-solving and reasoning abilities in the realm of mathematical problems, with difficulty maintained at a level equivalent to that of a fourth-grade elementary school.",
    "• CLUEWSC2020 (Xu et al, 2020b).",
    "The CLUEWSC2020 dataset serves as a Chinese rendition of the coreference resolution task, demanding models to assess the co-reference relationships within sentences involving pronouns or noun phrases.",
    "The sentences in the samples are meticulously chosen from 36 contemporary literary works and annotated by linguistic experts."
